title: Alfadhirhaiti
lyrics:
Draupnir
Geri Freki
Sleipnir
Gugnir
Haegolae Haegolae Haegolae Wiju Bi Gojze

Gaegogae Gaegogae Gaegogae Ginu Gahelija



Haugen Maunen



Ok Alfadhir heitir



Fimbulthulur Fjoelnir

Udhur Ulfroegni

Thekkur Thudur

Onski Ofnir

Rognir Raudhir

Grimnir Goendlir

Hlefreyr Hangatyr

Njolstapi Naudhvindir

Jolfudhr Jafnhaur

Atridhir Alfadhir

Sidgrani Sigfadhir

Dughirgjafi Dresvarpir

Bileygur Biflidhi

Margvisir Midhvitnis

Londungr Launhirdir

Yggr ok Yungir
